Math problem:
 In triangle $PQR$, we have $\angle P = 90^\circ$, $QR = 15$, and $\tan R = 5\cos Q$.  What is $PQ$?
XXXXX
Answer:
 [asy]
pair P,Q,R;
P = (0,0);
Q = (3*sqrt(24),0);
R = (0,3);
draw(P--Q--R--P);
draw(rightanglemark(Q,P,R,18));
